credit.credit-words: Great the heritage they left us, Great the conquests to be won, Arm√®d hosts to meet and scatter, Larger duties to be done. Raise the song they nobly taught us, Round the wide world let it ring: God is with us, God is with us, Christ our Lord shall reign as King!

Soon the struggle will be over, Soon the flags of strife be furled; Downward from his place, defeated, Shall the enemy be hurled; Onward, then, with ranks unbroken, Sure of triumph, shout and sing: God is with us, God is with us, Christ our Lord shall reign as King!
